  "description": "This individual is an undead human of late middle years, preserved in the salt-cured stagnation typical of grotto cadavers. Taupe skin is fissured and crusted along the jaw and knuckles, and gray eyes sit deep in shrunken sockets beneath a brow hardened into permanent strain. Black hair hangs in stringy, mineral-stiff locks, while the mouthline remains twisted into a fixed rictus that exposes worn teeth. The body carries the rigid, repetitive bearing of a remnant bound to place and habit, animated by a narrowed will and an unyielding watchfulness.",
